7.Write query to update comment message

      db.post.update(
      ...     {
      ...         post_id:1,
      ...         "comments.Comment_id":4
      ...     },
      ...     { $set: { 
      ...         "comments.$.message" : "This might be a good time to invest" 
      ...         }
      ...     }
      ... )
      WriteResult({ "nMatched" : 1, "nUpserted" : 0, "nModified" : 1 })
